TO RECOGNIZE THE MOTIVATION

35:30.462 --> 35:31.897
UNTIL LONG AFTER
YOU BOUGHT IT.

35:31.897 --> 35:33.465
WELL, BACK WHEN WE STARTED,

35:33.465 --> 35:35.334
I WAS JUST RICH,
NOT SUPER-RICH.

35:37.336 --> 35:39.338
YOU KNOW,
BEING A BILLIONAIRE...

35:41.707 --> 35:43.842
