YOU DIDN'T SMILE ENOUGH
DURING THE PRESSER.

40:02.467 --> 40:03.869
YOU LET THEM GET TO YOU.

40:03.869 --> 40:05.137
YOU'RE RIGHT.

40:05.137 --> 40:07.506
AND I DIDN'T LIKE THAT QUESTION
ABOUT AXE CAPITAL.

40:07.506 --> 40:08.540
WHAT PROMPTED THAT?

40:08.540 --> 40:09.941
SPYROS PLANTED IT.

40:09.941 --> 40:12.544
S.E.C. WANTS ME
TO MOVE ON AXE.

40:12.544 --> 40:14.980
IT'S DIFFICULT TO CONVICT
A POPULAR MAN.

40:14.980 --> 40:16.681
YES, I KNOW.

40:16.681 --> 40:19.818
WELL, IF YOU MOVE ON HIM
AND TAKE THAT RISK,

40:19.818 --> 40:21.620
YOU HAVE TO GET THE REWARD.

40:21.620 --> 40:24.456
YOU CAN LET THE S.E.C.
DO THE MOPPING UP,

40:24.456 --> 40:28.093
COLLECT THEIR FINES, BUT THEY
CAN'T BE SEEN AS LEADING IT.

40:28.093 --> 40:29.761
[ SCOFFS ]

40:29.761 --> 40:31.797
A LOT OF PEOPLE HAVE AXELROD'S
BACK IN THIS CITY.

40:31.797 --> 40:33.198
HE'S MADE THEM
A LOT OF MONEY.

40:33.198 --> 40:35.467
AND YOU KNOW THE LINE
IF YOU'RE GONNA STRIKE

40:35.467 --> 40:36.735
AGAINST THE KING.

40:36.735 --> 40:39.471
THE KING IS HOUSE SHOPPING
RIGHT NOW.

40:39.471 --> 40:41.439
PRIME BEACHFRONT, HERITAGE.

40:41.439 --> 40:42.808
HASN'T EVEN COME
ON MARKET YET.

40:42.808 --> 40:44.910
THAT'S A MISTAKE.

40:46.545 --> 40:50.849
A CONSPICUOUS BUY LIKE THAT
IN THE NEWS?

40:50.849 --> 40:53.852
HE GOES FROM A BILLIONAIRE
THAT YOU CAN PULL FOR

40:53.852 --> 40:55.754
TO JUST ANOTHER
RICH ASSHOLE.

40:55.754 --> 40:58.590
IF HE TURNS THE POPULOUS
AGAINST HIM,

40:58.590 --> 41:00.492
HE GIVES HIS EDGE TO YOU.

41:00.492 --> 41:04.229
I PASSED WORD THAT,
UH, HE SHOULDN'T BUY IT.

41:05.931 --> 41:08.800
IF HE'S INNOCENT, HE PASSES,

41:08.800 --> 41:10.936
BECAUSE HE'S A DISCIPLINED
PLAYER

41:10.936 --> 41:13.572
AND HE KNOWS THAT'S
THE DISCIPLINED MOVE.

41:13.572 --> 41:17.209
BUT A GUILTY MAN,
HE BUYS THAT HOUSE

41:17.209 --> 41:20.812
TO SHOW ME HE'S GOT
NOTHING TO HIDE.

41:20.812 --> 41:23.582
SMART.

41:23.582 --> 41:25.717
MAYBE I CAN HAVE A FRIEND
MAKE A BID,

41:25.717 --> 41:28.019
GET THE COMPETITIVE JUICES
FLOWING.

41:28.019 --> 41:29.120
I LIKE THAT.

41:29.120 --> 41:31.223
ROGER COULD ALWAYS USE
A NEW HOUSE.

41:31.223 --> 41:32.224
[ CHUCKLES ]

41:32.224 --> 41:35.827
AND I KNOW DENNY DANTONE
IS ACTIVELY LOOKING.

41:35.827 --> 41:37.562
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

41:37.562 --> 41:40.532
YOU GUYS KNOW
I ONLY DRAG FOOD INTO THIS ROOM

41:40.532 --> 41:41.800
FOR THE SUPER BOWL.

41:41.800 --> 41:43.735
COME ON, CHARLES.
I MADE THE POT PIES.

41:43.735 --> 41:45.503
I SHOULD HAVE SOME TIME
WITH MY SON.

41:45.503 --> 41:47.205
WE'LL BE RIGHT THERE.

41:49.074 --> 41:50.141
YOUR MOTHER.

41:50.141 --> 41:52.010
THAT'S A LOYAL WOMAN.

41:52.010 --> 41:53.111
DON'T.

41:53.111 --> 41:54.880
I'M JUST SAYING
THAT YOUR MOTHER

41:54.880 --> 41:56.848
WOULD NEVER LET
HER JOB INTERF--

41:56.848 --> 41:58.884
SHE NEVER LEFT
THE KITCHEN, DAD.

41:58.884 --> 42:01.887
THAT'S WHAT YOU WANTED
IN A WIFE, NOT ME.

42:01.887 --> 42:04.122
STILL, WENDY'S MAKING THINGS
DIFFICULT FOR YOU.

42:04.122 --> 42:05.757
WHY IS SHE STILL WORKING?

42:05.757 --> 42:07.826
WE STARTED TO DISCUSS IT.

42:07.826 --> 42:10.262
LEGALLY,
THERE'S NO CONFLICT YET.

42:10.262 --> 42:12.163
SHE'LL DO THE RIGHT THING.

42:12.163 --> 42:14.933
BETTER HOPE SO, SON.

42:16.902 --> 42:19.304
DANNY FUCKING MARGOLIS.
WHAT BRINGS YOU BACK?

42:19.304 --> 42:21.172
WHEN I SAW YOU
AT SUN VALLEY,

42:21.172 --> 42:24.042
YOU SAID YOU WERE HAPPY
AS A CLAM IN SHIT AT CENTURY.

42:24.042 --> 42:25.911
WELL, I AM.

42:25.911 --> 42:27.212
I WAS.

42:27.212 --> 42:28.780
YOU KNOW HOW IT IS.

42:28.780 --> 42:30.982
THINGS ARE GOOD THERE.

42:30.982 --> 42:32.817
I LIKE JERRY,
BUT I MISS THE FAMILY.

42:32.817 --> 42:34.085
WELL, YOU HAD TO GO IT
ON YOUR OWN

42:34.085 --> 42:35.687
WITH A BIGGER CHUNK
OF THE PIE.

42:35.687 --> 42:37.789
YEAH, TRUE.
[ CHUCKLES ]

42:37.789 --> 42:39.224
PLACE LOOKS GREAT,
BY THE WAY.

42:40.959 --> 42:43.728
IS THAT YOUR ROLLING ART
OUT FRONT?

42:43.728 --> 42:44.829
THE LAMBO?

42:47.332 --> 42:48.967
NO.

42:48.967 --> 42:50.902
I LIKE TO SIT TALL
IN THE SEAT.

42:50.902 --> 42:53.571
LOOK, UM,
I HAVE SOME IDEAS,

42:53.571 --> 42:55.273
AND I'D LOVE
TO SHARE THEM WITH YOU.

42:55.273 --> 42:58.009
I'D LOVE TO HEAR THEM.
COME TO THE NEXT DINNER.

42:58.009 --> 43:00.278
WE'LL BANG SOME STEAKS,
TALK SOME CONCEPTS.

43:00.278 --> 43:02.180
YEAH, OKAY. BUT I WAS JUST
HOPING THAT MAYBE, YOU KNOW --

43:02.180 --> 43:04.049
NO, I KNOW
WHAT YOU WERE HOPING.

43:05.150 --> 43:06.885
DOOR'S ALWAYS OPEN.

43:08.286 --> 43:09.988
YEAH.
YEAH, THAT'S COOL, BOBBY.

43:09.988 --> 43:11.990
I-I WILL.

43:11.990 --> 43:13.325
UH, TAKE CARE.

43:27.772 --> 43:29.240
[ KEYPAD BEEPS ]

43:34.679 --> 43:35.947
[ CAR ALARM CHIRPS ]

43:51.029 --> 43:54.132
HALL.
I NEED TO SEE YOU.

44:07.812 --> 44:08.980
THIS IS COZY.

44:08.980 --> 44:10.181
IT'S SECURE.

44:11.249 --> 44:13.952
I CHECKED WITH MY SOURCES
IN WASHINGTON.

44:13.952 --> 44:15.820
THERE'S NO CASE FILE
AGAINST YOU,

44:15.820 --> 44:18.289
BUT DAN MARGOLIS
WAS  ARRESTED.

44:18.289 --> 44:20.158
HE WAS RELEASED
ON HIS LAWYER'S RECOGNIZANCE,

44:20.158 --> 44:22.060
AND HIS ARRAIGNMENT'S
CURRENTLY ON HOLD.

44:22.060 --> 44:24.095
WHICH TELLS YOU WHAT?

44:24.095 --> 44:26.031
THAT HE'S COOPERATING.

44:27.832 --> 44:29.701
DID YOU HEAR IT OKAY?

44:29.701 --> 44:31.002
HOW THE HELL DID YOU KNOW?

44:31.002 --> 44:32.937
HE WAS MAKING
TOO MUCH EYE CONTACT.

44:32.937 --> 44:34.172
BARELY BLINKED.

44:34.172 --> 44:36.708
AND HIS PULSE WAS HAMMERING
LIKE HE WAS RUNNING A MARATHON.

44:36.708 --> 44:38.810
YOU WERE SMART
TO STAY QUIET.

44:38.810 --> 44:41.780
LOOK, THE S.E.C.
ISN'T THE THING.

44:41.780 --> 44:43.281
FINES ARE A PART OF LIFE.

44:43.281 --> 44:46.084
THE ATTACK YOU HAVE TO WORRY
ABOUT IS THE U.S. ATTORNEY'S.

44:46.084 --> 44:47.452
NOW, HERE'S WHAT
YOU'RE GONNA DO.

44:47.452 --> 44:50.221
ONE -- THAT REPORTER
FROM THE JOURNAL,

44:50.221 --> 44:53.291
THE ONE THAT WAS ASKING ABOUT
YOU, HE NEEDS TO BE HANDLED.

44:53.291 --> 44:56.461
I WOULD DO IT MYSELF,
BUT THEN HE'S OUT OF THE GAME.

44:56.461 --> 44:57.762
NO VALUE ADDED.

44:57.762 --> 45:00.098
BETTER IF YOU MAKE HIM
YOUR BEST FRIEND.

45:00.098 --> 45:04.269
AND TWO -- REMEMBER, YOU DON'T
HAVE TO OUTSWIM THE SHARK.

45:04.269 --> 45:08.406
YOU JUST HAVE TO OUTSWIM THE GUY
YOU'RE SCUBA DIVING WITH.

45:08.406 --> 45:09.808
YOU WANT ME TO DO THAT?

45:09.808 --> 45:11.409
YOU REMEMBER THAT NIGHT
IN REYKJAVIK?

45:11.409 --> 45:12.844
WISH I DIDN'T, BUT I DO.

45:12.844 --> 45:15.980
YOU SAID THERE WAS ONLY ONE
THING YOU WERE AFRAID OF.

45:17.048 --> 45:18.383
WINDBREAKERS.

45:18.383 --> 45:20.985
GUYS IN WINDBREAKERS
WALKING IN YOUR OFFICE SAYING,

45:20.985 --> 45:22.754
"STEP AWAY
FROM THE COMPUTER."

45:22.754 --> 45:25.023
AND YOU TOLD ME YOU'D MAKE SURE
IT WOULDN'T HAPPEN.

45:25.023 --> 45:27.125
SO, LET ME MAKE SURE.

45:28.326 --> 45:29.994
LOOK THERE.

45:32.263 --> 45:33.998
STEVEN BIRCH?

45:33.998 --> 45:35.400
IT'S EITHER HIM OR YOU.

45:36.868 --> 45:39.037
MEMORIZE THAT.

45:41.506 --> 45:45.443
WELL, IF IT'S GONNA BE SOMEONE,
IT MAY AS WELL BE THAT FRAUD.

45:45.443 --> 45:46.878
WE'RE SHARING THE STAGE

45:46.878 --> 45:49.481
AT THE DELIVERING ALPHA
CONFERENCE THIS WEEK.

45:51.249 --> 45:53.218
HE ACTS LIKE
HE'S MY BEST FRIEND

45:53.218 --> 45:55.353
DESPITE SHORT SQUEEZING ME
ON HMOs LAST YEAR.

45:56.921 --> 45:58.490
SO DO IT.

46:02.260 --> 46:03.461
HALL.

46:06.197 --> 46:09.033
WENDY RHOADES
TRIED TO QUIT TODAY.

46:10.235 --> 46:13.938
WE'VE BEEN FIGHTING BACK-TO-BACK
IN THE TRENCHES FOR 15 YEARS.

46:13.938 --> 46:15.807
BUT TODAY SHE TRIED TO QUIT.

46:15.807 --> 46:18.009
STILL TRUST HER?

46:18.009 --> 46:20.512
I WANT TO.

46:25.216 --> 46:27.819
I DIDN'T KNOW THIS PLACE
WAS OPEN FOR LUNCH.

46:27.819 --> 46:28.887
IT'S NOT.

46:28.887 --> 46:30.889
THANKS, TONY.

46:30.889 --> 46:32.957
MY PLEASURE,
MR. AXELROD.

46:32.957 --> 46:34.359
WE'RE OFF THE RECORD.

46:34.359 --> 46:36.828
IF YOU FUCK ME,
I NEVER TALK TO YOU AGAIN.

46:36.828 --> 46:37.996
GOT IT.

46:37.996 --> 46:41.132
GOOD. IF YOU EVER WANT TO
COME HERE, JUST CALL ME.

46:42.300 --> 46:44.169
NOW, WHY WAS MY NAME
COMING OUT OF YOUR MOUTH

46:44.169 --> 46:45.203
AT A PRESS CONFERENCE?

46:45.203 --> 46:46.938
HEY, THAT WAS BEFORE
YOU ASKED ME TO LUNCH.

46:49.274 --> 46:51.075
JUMP IN.

46:51.075 --> 46:53.244
LET'S TALK ABOUT THOSE KIDS
YOU PUT THROUGH COLLEGE.

46:53.244 --> 46:56.281
THAT'S THE ONE QUESTION GETS ME
WALKING AWAY FROM THE TABLE.

46:56.281 --> 46:57.549
THAT'S BETWEEN
THEM AND ME.

46:57.549 --> 46:59.217
I DON'T TALK ABOUT IT
WITH ANYONE ELSE.

47:05.156 --> 47:07.058
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

47:07.058 --> 47:09.360
BON APPÃ©TIT.

47:09.360 --> 47:10.595
WHAT'S NEXT?

47:10.595 --> 47:12.864
SOFTBALL. UNDERHAND.

47:12.864 --> 47:15.400
GIVE ME SOME INSIGHT INTO HOW
YOU PROCESS INFORMATION.

47:15.400 --> 47:18.436
THE PRESS ACTS LIKE
INFORMATION'S A DIRTY WORD.

47:18.436 --> 47:20.538
EVERYONE HAS ACCESS
TO THE INFORMATION.

47:20.538 --> 47:23.074
WE JUST KNOW HOW
TO ANALYZE IT BETTER.

47:23.074 --> 47:25.243
YOU ANSWER ME ONE.

47:25.243 --> 47:28.413
WHEN DID IT BECOME A CRIME
TO SUCCEED IN THIS COUNTRY?

47:28.413 --> 47:30.615
AMERICA USED TO SALUTE
THE GUY IN THE LIMOUSINE.

47:30.615 --> 47:32.483
THEY WANTED TO BE THE GUY
IN THE LIMOUSINE.

47:32.483 --> 47:33.451
THEY STILL WANT TO.

47:33.451 --> 47:35.053
BUT NOW THEY THROW
EGGS AT IT.

47:35.053 --> 47:37.956
I ONLY EVER WENT
EGGING ONCE.

47:37.956 --> 47:39.958
BIGGEST HOUSE
IN THE NEIGHBORHOOD,

47:39.958 --> 47:42.493
AND THEY NEVER GAVE OUT
ANY CANDY, SO THEY DESERVED IT.

47:42.493 --> 47:44.395
WE DESTROYED THAT PLACE.

47:44.395 --> 47:46.497
ONCE?
YOU'RE AN ALTAR BOY.

47:46.497 --> 47:48.366
THAT WAS EVERY HALLOWEEN
FOR ME.

47:48.366 --> 47:49.901
YOU'RE FROM AROUND
HERE, RIGHT?

47:49.901 --> 47:52.303
YEAH, GRAND CONCOURSE.
THEN WHITE PLAINS.

47:52.303 --> 47:55.139
YEAH, ME TOO. WELL, YONKERS,
BUT IT WASN'T NICE BACK THEN.

47:55.139 --> 47:56.274
HEY, MAN, YONKERS
USED TO BE A PLACE

47:56.274 --> 47:57.875
WHERE YOU COULD
REALLY GET YOUR ASS KICKED.

47:57.875 --> 47:59.377
[ CHUCKLES ]

47:59.377 --> 48:01.613
YOU'RE A GOOD KID
FOR A FUCKING HACK.

48:01.613 --> 48:04.249
AND YOU'RE A GOOD GUY
FOR A BANKSTER.

48:04.249 --> 48:06.484
ALL RIGHT, FUCK IT.

48:06.484 --> 48:08.052
I WASN'T GONNA GIVE YOU THIS,

48:08.052 --> 48:11.089
BUT YOU'RE HERE FOR A STORY
AND NOW I LIKE YOU, SO...

48:12.156 --> 48:13.291
...STEVEN BIRCH.

48:13.291 --> 48:14.359
PIEDMONT CAPITAL.

48:14.359 --> 48:15.927
YEAH.

48:15.927 --> 48:18.463
THAT SWAP DEAL HE DID
ON ARCADIAN RAILROAD...

48:18.463 --> 48:20.932
THE TIMING IS VERY CURIOUS.

48:20.932 --> 48:22.133
WHAT KIND OF SWAP?

48:22.133 --> 48:24.302
I'M NOT GONNA WRITE
THE ARTICLE FOR YOU.

48:24.302 --> 48:27.472
DO AN AUTOPSY ON THE DEAL,

48:27.472 --> 48:30.208
YOU'LL FIND YOURSELF A PULITZER
IN THE CARCASS.

48:33.911 --> 48:35.480
HERE'S MY CELL.

48:35.480 --> 48:39.917
DON'T CALL
UNTIL THE MARKET CLOSES.

48:39.917 --> 48:41.619
NO VOICEMAIL.

48:42.654 --> 48:45.256
NO E-MAIL.
UNDERSTOOD.

48:46.958 --> 48:48.626
ENJOY YOUR LUNCH.

48:54.332 --> 48:57.235
David: HOW DO YOU RESPOND TO
THE CRITICISM THAT HEDGE FUNDS

48:57.235 --> 48:59.370
ARE THE SCAVENGERS
OF THE FINANCIAL SECTOR

48:59.370 --> 49:03.074
AND THAT A SELECT FEW HAVE
UNDUE INFLUENCE ON THE MARKETS?

49:03.074 --> 49:06.244
ANY PUBLIC STATEMENT YOU MAKE
OR POSITION YOU TAKE

49:06.244 --> 49:08.246
CAN SEND A STOCK SOARING
OR FALLING.

49:08.246 --> 49:10.114
WE'RE NOT SCAVENGERS.

49:10.114 --> 49:12.950
WE'RE WHITE BLOOD CELLS
SCRUBBING OUT BAD COMPANIES,

49:12.950 --> 49:15.053
EARNING FOR OUR INVESTORS,
PREVENTING BUBBLES.

49:15.053 --> 49:16.120
EXCUSE ME.

49:16.120 --> 49:18.022
A HEDGE FUND LIKE MINE
IS A MARKET REGULATOR.

49:18.022 --> 49:20.491
I WANT PEOPLE LIKE BOBBY AXELROD
ON THAT WALL.

49:20.491 --> 49:22.393
I NEED THEM ON THAT WALL.

49:22.393 --> 49:25.997
AXE MAKES MY LIFE EASIER BY
SHOUTING IF HE SEES SOMETHING.

49:25.997 --> 49:28.099
THE MOMENT I LET SOMEONE
IN A BOARDROOM...

49:30.335 --> 49:34.539
...OR A GOVERNMENT OFFICE TELL
ME WHAT I CAN OR CANNOT BUY,

49:34.539 --> 49:38.209
I MAY AS WELL CLOSE THE SHOP,
AND I'M NOT CLOSING THE SHOP.

49:38.209 --> 49:41.045
LET'S TOUCH ON THE ROLE
OF THE ACTIVIST INVESTOR

49:41.045 --> 49:42.113
IN TODAY'S MARKET.

49:42.113 --> 49:43.581
I'M NOT JUST PLAYING FOR MYSELF.

49:43.581 --> 49:45.249
I'M PLAYING FOR ALL
SHAREHOLDERS,

49:45.249 --> 49:47.385
LIKE MY GOOD FRIEND
STEVEN BIRCH HERE.

49:47.385 --> 49:50.388
BOBBY AXELROD, STEVEN BIRCH,
THANKS TO YOU BOTH.

49:50.388 --> 49:53.057
[ APPLAUSE ]

50:02.066 --> 50:04.736
UM, THAT, UH, THING
WE WERE TALKING ABOUT,

50:04.736 --> 50:07.071
THEY ARE LEVERED
FOUR TO ONE.

50:07.071 --> 50:09.040
WHEN THEIR ACCOUNTING
COMES OUT,

50:09.040 --> 50:10.708
IT'S NOT GONNA LOOK PRETTY,
RIGHT?

50:10.708 --> 50:13.511
THOSE FUCKING GUYS.
I WASN'T TOLD.

50:13.511 --> 50:15.780
I DON'T KNOW WHY BROOKS
SAVED THOSE SEATS FOR THEM.

50:15.780 --> 50:17.382
I'M GONNA FIND HIM
AND SKIN HIS ASS.

50:17.382 --> 50:18.449
ENOUGH.

50:18.449 --> 50:19.650
I'M GONNA GET ME
THAT SCALP.

50:19.650 --> 50:21.719
YOU CRUSHED IT.
CRUSHED.

50:21.719 --> 50:23.187
LET'S GET OUT
OF THIS RAT FUCK.

50:25.757 --> 50:28.493
WATCH OUT.
HE MAY BUY THE BUILDING.

50:28.493 --> 50:30.495
IT'S AN A-MINUS BUILDING.
NEEDS OVERHAUL.

50:30.495 --> 50:32.697
HE DOESN'T CONSIDER ANYTHING
LESS THAN TRIPLE-A.

50:32.697 --> 50:34.365
YET HE HIRED YOU.

50:34.365 --> 50:35.500
EASY, BRYAN.

50:35.500 --> 50:36.801
LEARN ANYTHING
FROM MY TALK?

50:36.801 --> 50:39.303
VOLUMES.
YOU STAYING FOR MINE?

50:39.303 --> 50:41.038
I KNOW YOUR ACT.

50:41.038 --> 50:42.473
[ LAUGHS ]

50:42.473 --> 50:45.543
YOU SENDING ME MESSAGES?
'CAUSE I'M HERE.

50:47.578 --> 50:49.680
WELL, THE KIDS
IN MY OFFICE

50:49.680 --> 50:51.716
REALLY THOUGHT
YOU MIGHT BUY THAT HOUSE.

50:51.716 --> 50:54.585
I TOLD THEM
YOU GOT BIG BALLS,

50:54.585 --> 50:56.587
BUT NOT THAT BIG.

50:56.587 --> 50:58.723
YEAH, RIGHT.
I'LL PROBABLY PASS.

51:00.291 --> 51:02.226
IT'S SO NICE, THOUGH,
YOU KNOW.

51:02.226 --> 51:05.496
FEELS LIKE YOU'RE PART
OF THE BEACH AND OCEAN.

51:05.496 --> 51:07.832
AND ALL THAT AIR OUT THERE...

51:07.832 --> 51:10.568
SHIT, YOU KNOW ABOUT IT.

51:10.568 --> 51:12.370
YOUR DADDY'S GOT
A LITTLE PLACE OUT THERE.

51:12.370 --> 51:15.606
HE MUST LET YOU USE A BEDROOM
SOME WEEKENDS IF YOU SAY PLEASE.

51:15.606 --> 51:16.741
WALK AWAY.

51:17.842 --> 51:19.343
I SHOULD.

51:19.343 --> 51:22.780
BUT THEN AGAIN, WHAT'S THE POINT
OF HAVING "FUCK YOU" MONEY

51:22.780 --> 51:25.349
IF YOU NEVER SAY
"FUCK YOU"?

51:27.118 --> 51:29.520
YOU'RE A SMART MAN.

51:29.520 --> 51:32.223
SO YOU KNOW
WHEN I BRING AN ACTION,

51:32.223 --> 51:35.393
NOT SOME COUNTY
OR EVEN STATE,

51:35.393 --> 51:37.795
IT'S THE UNITED STATES
VERSUS.

51:37.795 --> 51:40.097
DON'T GIVE ME
A REASON.

51:40.097 --> 51:42.133
OH, I KNOW WHO BRINGS
AN ACTION.

51:43.134 --> 51:46.537
AND I KNOW WHAT YOU FEEL ABOUT
YOUR PERFECT RECORD, TOO.

51:46.537 --> 51:49.807
YOU CAN'T AFFORD A MARK
IN THE LOSS COLUMN.

51:49.807 --> 51:52.810
THERE'S A SAYING
IN BASEBALL.

51:52.810 --> 51:55.580
TOWNS FIRE MANAGERS.

51:55.580 --> 51:58.182
OWNERS JUST GIVE THEM
THE BAD NEWS.

51:58.182 --> 52:02.186
YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE RUNNING
THE BIG MONEY THEY CHEER FOR.

52:02.186 --> 52:04.422
BUT THAT'S BECAUSE
YOU WORKED THAT 9/11 SHIT

52:04.422 --> 52:05.423
FOR ALL IT'S WORTH.

52:05.423 --> 52:06.824
FUCK YOURSELF.

52:08.292 --> 52:11.128
I HAVE NEVER SENT OUT
A SINGLE PRESS RELEASE,

52:11.128 --> 52:12.864
GIVEN ONE INTERVIEW.

52:12.864 --> 52:15.800
I LOST EVERY ONE OF MY FRIENDS
THAT DAY.

52:15.800 --> 52:18.369
AND YOU'VE MANAGED
TO MAKE SOME NEW ONES SINCE.

52:20.571 --> 52:24.775
BUT LIKE I SAID,
THEY MAY BE CHEERING NOW,

52:24.775 --> 52:29.380
BUT BELIEVE ME,
THEY ARE DYING TO BOO.

52:30.781 --> 52:32.884
Moderator:
AND NOW FROM THE OTHER SIDE,

52:32.884 --> 52:36.754
THE MAN WHOSE JOB IS TO RIDE
HERD OVER THE BULLS AND BEARS,

52:36.754 --> 52:38.623
CHUCK RHOADES.

52:38.623 --> 52:42.260
[ APPLAUSE ]

52:55.806 --> 52:58.175
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATING ]

53:00.678 --> 53:01.946
YEAH.

